2024: Appeared against Bucknell… had one shot

2023: Has not seen game action

Prior to West Point: From Novato, CA... Adrenaline All-American… Varsity Lacrosse at Novato High School (2x captain)… 3 years varsity basketball… Outstanding member of St. Anthony’s church… Community service with the church… Participated in fundraiser that supported Leukemia research… The Big Vince.
